summary: A little simple mod showing what happens in Skyrim after the Dunmers arrived.
descriptionHtml:
Children of both Norths and Dunmer, they are a tall and dark skinned people. Strong and hardy, Dark Half Elves are known for their resistance to both cold and fire aswell as their talent as both warriors and thieves. They can use a Battlecry to make opponents flee.

Technical:
I used the Nord Race as a base and changed the morph and coloursettings.
Onehanded 10
Destruction 5
Sneak 5
Alchemy 5
Speech 5
Ligth armor 5
Ymir\'s Blessing 30% resistance to both Frost and Fire
Nords Battlecry

New Version
Added all dunmer hair and eye-colour. Created new Presets for the race based on the Nords Presets. Also added some Nord skin-colour.

Edit:
Working on a update or a new mod that involves the rest of the elves. There migth be a total new mod with a new idea that also solves the identity issue. Work in progress
